title: Facebook's Oculus unveils new virtual reality headset
text: CNBC's Josh Lipton reports from the 2019 Game Developers Conference with Oculus' new VR headset along with a set of new games to accompany it.

title: Facebook: Here We Go Again
text: Over the last year, Facebook has been on a roller coaster ride due to issues with data privacy concerns.

title: Facebook shows it's still serious about virtual reality with new $399 headset
text: Facebook announced the Oculus Rift S after reports last year that the company had no plans to upgrade its PC-connected virtual reality headset.

title: Facebook to change its ad-targeting options to prevent discrimination
text: Facebook is making some big changes on how it targets ads to users in face of anger from both sides of the political aisle. CNBC's Julia Boorstin reports.
